edu.ucsb.cs56.pconrad.parsing.syntax

Interface ASTFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultASTFactory

    public interface ASTFactory
    Decouples token constructors and underlying class hierarchy from how AST nodes behave. Only used in the test suites for the parser and the evaluator. Uses the Factory method design pattern.
